Text:
Salah satu cara aku guna untuk simpan+belanja adalah gunakan threshold. 

Contoh threshold RM10k, kalau duit lebih sikit banding threshold tu, aku akan belanja. Once hit, aku consider myself as 'broke'.

Every year aku cuba naikkan threshold supaya boleh reach retirement goal.
Translated Text:
One of the ways I use it to save + shop is to use a threshold.

For example, a threshold of RM10k, if there is less money than that threshold, I will shop. Once hit, I consider myself as 'broke'.

Every year I try to raise the threshold so that I can reach my retirement goal.

Text:
Walaupun saya nyatakan senarai di atas, jika boleh elak membeli iPhone yang tamat pengeluaran yang berkemungkinan stok lama.

Although I mentioned the list above, if possible avoid buying an expired iPhone which is likely to be old stock.

The list above is for reference if you want to buy an iPhone.

Text:
Perlu diingatkan, kenyataan di atas tidak merujuk kepada pengguna yang telah memiliki mana-mana model iPhone.

Senarai di atas adalah berdasarkan perspektif peribadi saya semata-mata.
Translated Text:
It should be noted, the statement above does not refer to users who already own any iPhone model.

The above list is based solely on my personal perspective.

Text:
Jika anda ingin membeli iPhone set terpakai, berhati-hati kerana dikhuatiri terkandung komponen tiruan yang boleh memudaratkan iPhone.

Segelintir Penjual tidak akan mendedahkan status keaslian iPhone tersebut dan menjadi tanggungjawab anda untuk bertanya dan menyiasat.
Translated Text:
If you want to buy a used iPhone set, be careful because it is feared that it contains fake components that can harm the iPhone.

Few Sellers will not disclose the authenticity status of the iPhone and it is your responsibility to ask and investigate.

Text:
Jika anda benar-benar ingin mengetahui status keaslian iPhone, sila hantar ke AASP untuk diagnostik.

Pihak AASP akan mengeluarkan laporan menyeluruh sama ada iPhone tersebut benar-benar asli atau sebaliknya.
Translated Text:
If you really want to know the original status of your iPhone, please send it to AASP for diagnostics.

The AASP will issue a comprehensive report whether the iPhone is truly genuine or vice versa.

Text:
Saya yakin rekaan Neumorphism akan diperkenalkan pada iOS. Ini dibuktikan dengan transisi macOS Big Sur kepada Neumorphism. 

Jika dilihat dari sudut sejarah sekalipun, Apple telah memperkenalkan rekaan baharu pada  OS X Yosemite yang diinspirasikan daripada iOS 7.
Translated Text:
I'm sure the Neumorphism design will be introduced on iOS. This is evidenced by the transition of macOS Big Sur to Neumorphism.

If viewed from a historical perspective, Apple has introduced a new design on OS X Yosemite inspired by iOS 7.

Text:
Sudah pasti iOS akan datang bakal hadir dengan rekaan Neumorphism. 

Apple sebelum ini telah membunuh rekaan Skeuomorph yang diperkenalkan oleh Scott Forstall. Maka sudah masanya rekaan flat ditukar kepada Neumorphism.
Translated Text:
It is certain that the upcoming iOS will come with a Neumorphism design.

Apple had previously killed the Skeuomorph design introduced by Scott Forstall. So it's time to change the flat design to Neumorphism.

Text: Saya tidak berikan harapan. Namun percaya iOS 16 bakal menjadi iOS pertama memperkenalkan antara muka baharu yang diambil daripada Neumorphism.
Translated Text: I do not give hope. But believe that iOS 16 will be the first iOS to introduce a new interface taken from Neumorphism.

Just my view 😊

Text:
Saya tertarik untuk mengulas tentang twit yang dikongsi oleh @pikyahan. 

Memang diakui jangka hayat bateri Apple Watch hanya bertahan kurang 18 jam tertakluk kepada penggunaan.
Translated Text:
I am interested to comment on the tweet shared by @pikyahan.

It is admitted that the battery life of the Apple Watch only lasts less than 18 hours subject to use.

Text:
Sebelum jatuh hukum mengapa jangka hayat bateri Apple Watch tidak seperti jam pintar yang lain. 

Kita perlu menilai dalam pelbagai aspek termasuklah perkakasan, perisian dan cara penggunaan.
Translated Text:
Before falling into law why the battery life of the Apple Watch is not like other smart watches.

We need to evaluate in various aspects including hardware, software and the way of use.

Text:
Terdapat segelintir warga maya membandingkan Apple Watch dengan Mi Watch Lite. 

Mi Watch Lite mampu bertahan sehingga sembilan hari berbanding Apple Watch yang hanya bertahan kurang dua hari. https://t.co/SymAqNRo6n
Translated Text:
There are quite a few netizens comparing the Apple Watch with the Mi Watch Lite.

Mi Watch Lite can last up to nine days compared to Apple Watch which only lasts less than two days. https://t.co/SymAqNRo6n

Text: Perlu diingatkan, perisian Apple Watch menggunakan watchOS berbanding Mi Watch Lite menggunakan sistem pengendalian  mereka yang tidak dinyatakan secara terperinci.
Translated Text: It should be noted, Apple Watch software uses watchOS compared to Mi Watch Lite using their operating system which is not specified in detail.

Text: Jika kita melihat dari segi paparan anta muka serta pengalaman penggunaan, watchOS boleh dianggap sistem operasi terbaik berbanding yang digunakan pada Mi Watch Lite.
Translated Text: If we look in terms of interface display and user experience, watchOS can be considered the best operating system compared to the one used on Mi Watch Lite.

Text:
watchOS seperti iOS, setiap tahun mempunyai versi baharu yang bukan sekadar tangkap muat. 

watchOS memerlukan kuasa yang tinggi bagi memastikan sistem pengendalian dapat beroperasi sepenuhnya.
Translated Text:
watchOS like iOS, every year has a new version that isn't just a catch-up.

watchOS requires high power to ensure the operating system is fully operational.

Text:
Contoh paling mudah, mengapa bateri Nokia 3310 (2017) mampu bertahan lebih lama berbanding iPhone 8 sedangkan mAh bagi Nokia 3310 hanya 1,200 sahaja. 

Ini disebabkan Nokia tidak memerlukan kuasa tinggi untuk menjalankan sistem pengendalian mereka sendiri. https://t.co/PXZlFP28s3
Translated Text:
The simplest example is why the Nokia 3310 (2017) battery can last longer than the iPhone 8 when the mAh for the Nokia 3310 is only 1,200.

This is because Nokia does not need high power to run their own operating system. https://t.co/PXZlFP28s3

Text:
Pemilihan sesebuah jam pintar bukan sekadar melihat pada bateri semata-mata. Kita perlu membuat perbandingan dalam pelbagai aspek. 

Saya akui Garmin Venu 2S sebagai contoh mampu bertahan selama sepuluh hari. https://t.co/LpZ4msDpLn
Translated Text:
Choosing a smart watch is not just about looking at the battery. We need to make comparisons in various aspects.

I admit the Garmin Venu 2S for example can last for ten days. https://t.co/LpZ4msDpLn

Text:
Adakah semua selesa dengan sistem pengendalian yang digunakan?

Menurut laporan @CounterPointTR, Apple Watch menduduki tangga pertama dengan menguasai 28% berbanding Garmin yang hanya 5.8%. 

Adakah membeli Apple Watch satu keputusan yang salah? https://t.co/4z5l6REuBG
Translated Text:
Is everyone comfortable with the operating system being used?

According to a @CounterPointTR report, Apple Watch occupies the first place with 28% compared to Garmin which is only 5.8%.

Is buying an Apple Watch a wrong decision? https://t.co/4z5l6REuBG

Text:
Terdapat beberapa perkara lain perlu dinilai secara  tuntas dan jangan kerana bateri semua perkara baik dianaktirikan. 

Aksesori Apple Watch hakikatnya sangat mudah untuk didapati dalam atau luar talian.
Translated Text:
There are some other things that need to be thoroughly evaluated and not because the battery is all good things.

Apple Watch accessories are actually very easy to find online or offline.

Text:
Jika dibandingkan dengan Garmin, saya yakin tali jam Apple Watch lebih mudah dan banyak didapati dengan pelbagai pilihan. 

Apple Watch terkini juga sudah menyokong ECG. Selain itu Apple Watch turut hadir fitur O2, Bunyi, Penjejakan Kitaran Haid,Kecergasan dan lain-lain.
Translated Text:
Compared to Garmin, I'm sure the Apple Watch strap is easier and more available with a variety of options.

The latest Apple Watch also already supports ECG. In addition, Apple Watch also features O2, Sound, Menstrual Cycle Tracking, Fitness and others.

Text:
Konklusinya, bateri bukanlah prasyarat untuk seseorang itu membeli sebuah jam pintar. 

Jika hanya fokus pada bateri, banyak jam pintar lain yang ada di pasaran. Walakin begitu, mereka tidak hanya fokus pada bateri semata-mata.
Translated Text:
In conclusion, battery is not a prerequisite for someone to buy a smart watch.

If you only focus on the battery, there are many other smart watches on the market. However, they don't just focus on the battery alone.

Text:
Reka bentuk sudah pasti menjadi keutamaan walaupun perkara ini subjektif untuk dibincangkan. 

Bagaimana Apple Watch segerak (sync) dengan iPhone juga menjadi pilihan memandangkan ia dalam ekosistem yang sama.
Translated Text:
Design is definitely a priority although this is subjective to discuss.

How the Apple Watch synchronizes (sync) with the iPhone is also an option considering that it is in the same ecosystem.

Text:
Isu bateri hakikatnya bukan semata-mata tertumpu kepada jam pintar. Sebelum ini ramai warga maya menyindir pengguna iPhone kerana sering membawa bank kuasa (power bank). 

Mengapa orang tetap membelinya sedangkan Android mempunyai bateri yang tahan lebih lama?
Translated Text:
The battery issue is actually not only focused on smart watches. Previously, many virtual citizens mocked iPhone users for often carrying a power bank.

Why do people keep buying it when Android has a longer lasting battery?

Text:
Sokongan watchOS juga antara terbaik dalam pasaran. Berbeza dengan wearOS daripada Android yang saya lihat tidak agresif berbanding Apple. 

Mengapa saya tidak banding dengan Garmin? Sistem operasi Garmin tidak seperti watchOS atau wearOS.
Translated Text:
The watchOS support is also among the best in the market. Unlike wearOS from Android which I see is not aggressive compared to Apple.

Why don't I compare to Garmin? Garmin's operating system is not like watchOS or wearOS.

Text:
Jika anda lihat pasaran jam pintar terpakai, permintaan Apple Watch jauh lebih tinggi berbanding  jam pintar yang lain. 

Susut nilai Apple Watch juga tidak begitu ketara berbanding jam pintar yang lain.
Translated Text:
If you look at the used smartwatch market, demand for Apple Watch is much higher than other smartwatches.

The depreciation of the Apple Watch is also not so significant compared to other smart watches.

Text:
Sudah jadi kelaziman produk Apple bakal menjadi buah mulut sesetengah warga maya. 

Tidak kira iPhone, Apple Watch, AirPods atau apa-apa produk sekalipun tetap menjadi sasaran.
Translated Text:
It is common for Apple products to become the talk of some virtual citizens.

It doesn't matter if the iPhone, Apple Watch, AirPods or whatever product is still being targeted.

Text:
Saya tidak katakan Apple Watch tidak mempunyai keburukan. Tiada produk yang sempurna, cuma ingin mengubah cara kita berfikir dan bukan semata-mata tertumpu kepada satu perkara tanpa melihat yang tersirat. 

SEKADAR PANDANGAN
Translated Text:
I'm not saying the Apple Watch doesn't have its downsides. There is no perfect product, just want to change the way we think and not just focus on one thing without seeing what is implied.

JUST A VIEW

Text:
AirPods menggunakan bateri ion litium, Apple tidak memperincikan kitaran bateri bagi produk ini. 

Kendatipun begitu, berdasarkan maklum balas daripada pengguna, kebiasaannya bateri mula menyusut selepas 24 bulan.
Translated Text:
AirPods use lithium ion batteries, Apple does not detail the battery cycle for this product.

However, based on feedback from users, the battery usually begins to shrink after 24 months.

Text:
Walakin begitu, semua bergantung kepada cara kita menjaga kesihatan bateri. 

Pastikan bateri AirPods tidak capai 0% serta elak daripada panas atau sejuk melampau.
Translated Text:
However, it all depends on how we take care of battery health.

Make sure the AirPods battery does not reach 0% and avoid extreme heat or cold.

Text:
AirPods juga turut hadir dengan fitur Pengecasan Bateri Optimum yang membolehkan pengecasan terhenti saat 80% bagi menjaga kesihatan bateri. 

Pastikan juga anda kemas kini perisian tegar pada versi terkini.
Translated Text:
AirPods also come with an Optimum Battery Charging feature that allows charging to stop at 80% to maintain battery health.

Also make sure you update the firmware to the latest version.

Text:
Hakikatnya majoriti produk seperti ini sukar untuk diganti dengan bateri baharu. 

Jangan fikir hanya AirPods sahaja produk pakai buang. Hakikatnya banyak produk sama yang berlainan jenama mempunyai isu yang sama.
Translated Text:
The fact is that the majority of products like this are difficult to replace with new batteries.

Don't think only AirPods are disposable products. The fact is that many of the same products from different brands have the same issue.

Text: Faktor harga serta jenama Apple yang sering menjadi sasaran menyebabkan segelintir pihak berpandangan hanya AirPods sahaja mempunyai masalah seperti ini.
Translated Text: The price factor as well as the Apple brand which is often the target cause some parties to think that only AirPods have this kind of problem.

Text:
Hawkeye mengisahkan tentang pembentukan karakter Kate Bishop, konflik Ronin serta penglibatan Kingpin. 

Walakin begitu, Hawkeye saya letakkan kedudukan terendah dalam rancangan TV berbanding judul yang lain.
Translated Text:
Hawkeye tells the story of Kate Bishop's character development, the Ronin conflict and the Kingpin's involvement.

However, I rank Hawkeye the lowest in TV shows compared to other titles.

Text:
Berikut kedudukan rancangan TV berdasarkan perspektif saya:

1. Loki
2. WandaVision
3. What If...?
4. The Falcon and the Winter Soldier
5. Hawkeye 

Berbeza dengan rancangan TV yang lain, Hawkeye tidak mempunyai pengakhiran kredit akhir yang berkait dengan MCU.
Translated Text:
Here is the ranking of TV shows based on my perspective:

1. Loki
2. WandaVision
3. What If...?
4. The Falcon and the Winter Soldier
5. Hawkeye

Unlike other TV shows, Hawkeye does not have an MCU-related end credits ending.

Text:
Secara keseluruhan saya suka menonton semua rancangan TV daripada MCU. 

Diharapkan tahun hadapan MCU dapat sajikan rancangan TV yang lebih berkualiti. 

Skala Hawkeye : 6.5/10
Translated Text:
Overall I love watching all the TV shows from the MCU.

It is hoped that MCU will be able to present better quality TV shows next year.

Hawkeye Scale : 6.5/10

Text:
Saya tidak akan memperincikan jalan cerita cuma ingin berkongsi pengalaman setelah menonton filem ini.

Sejujurnya Spider-Man: No Way Home merupakan filem terbaik berbanding Spider-Man: Far from Home dan Spider-Man: Homecoming.
Translated Text:
I won't go into detail about the story, just want to share my experience after watching this movie.

To be honest, Spider-Man: No Way Home is the best movie compared to Spider-Man: Far from Home and Spider-Man: Homecoming.

Text: Filem ini telah membuatkan saya tertawa, sedih serta tergamam. Jika sebelum ini watak Peter Parker sinonim dengan Tony Stark. Tidak keberatan jika saya katakan Peter Parker dan Doctor Strange sangat secocok.
Translated Text: This movie has made me laugh, sad and stunned. If previously the character of Peter Parker was synonymous with Tony Stark. Don't mind if I say Peter Parker and Doctor Strange are a great match.

Text:
Jangan lupa terdapat dua kredit pada pengakhiran penceritaan.

Bagi saya kredit kedua filem ini telah membuatkan saya terdiam dan ternanti akan filem seterusnya. Saya anggap filem ini antara yang terbaik dalam naskhah Marvel Cinematic Universe.

Skala:8/10
Translated Text:
Don't forget there are two credits at the end of the narration.

For me, the second credit of this movie has left me speechless and looking forward to the next movie. I consider this movie to be one of the best in the Marvel Cinematic Universe.

Scale: 8/10

Text:
Aman mencuba nasib bekerja sebagai pemandu e-panggilan (e-hailing). 

Walakin begitu, disebabkan dia buta warna serta memiliki kereta yang uzur. Aman terpaksa menggunakan khidmat orang tengah bagi membolehkan dia bekerja secara "halal".
Translated Text:
Aman tried his luck working as an e-hailing driver.

However, because he is color blind and owns a dilapidated car. Aman had to use the services of a middleman to enable him to work "halal".

Text:
Kehidupan Aman di Kuala Lumpur tidaklah seindah yang disangka. Pelbagai coretan diceritakan dalam filem ini. 

Prebet Sapu telah membongkar wajah sebenar Kuala Lumpur yang dianggap syurga dunia.
Translated Text:
Aman's life in Kuala Lumpur is not as beautiful as expected. Various snippets are told in this film.

Private Sapu has uncovered the true face of Kuala Lumpur, which is considered the world's paradise.

Text:
Sisi gelap ini diterjemah melalui setiap ceritera yang berlaku sewaktu Aman berkhidmat sebagai e-panggilan. 

Saya tidak akan memperincikan jalan cerita, cuma apa yang ditunjukkan dalam filem ini sebuah kenyataan yang tidak boleh disangkal.
Translated Text:
This dark side is translated through every story that happens when Aman serves as an e-call.

I won't go into detail about the plot, just what is shown in this movie is an undeniable fact.

Text:
Kisah ini berlaku sewaktu negara sedang menghadapi Pilihanraya umum ke-14.

Selain kehidupan Aman, kita juga boleh melihat sisi gelap ahli politik yang sering kita agungkan.
Translated Text:
This story happened when the country was facing the 14th general election.

In addition to Aman's life, we can also see the dark side of politicians that we often glorify.

Text:
Banyak perkara yang terungkai hingga kita tidak percaya ia benar-benar berlaku yang hakikatnya berlaku. 

Keindahan yang kita lihat hanya sebuah lakaran. Saya bersyukur kerana bukan salah seorang seperti Aman.
Translated Text:
Many things are unraveled until we don't believe it really happened which actually happened.

The beauty we see is just a sketch. I am thankful that I am not one of those people like Aman.

Text:
Filem ini turut menceritakan kehidupan Bella seorang gadis yang berasal dari Pulau Pinang datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mengubah kehidupan. 

Kehidupan Bella sama seperti Aman, tiada tempat untuk bergantung dan hanya bertahan untuk hidup.
Translated Text:
This film also tells the life of Bella, a girl from Penang who came to Kuala Lumpur to change her life.

Bella's life is the same as Aman's, nowhere to depend on and just hanging on to live.

Text:
Filem ini ditayangkan dalam hitam putih yang saya anggap mempunyai kaitan dengan Aman seorang buta warna. 

Sejujurnya filem ini mempunyai peminat tersendiri dan bukan semua boleh menerima akan jalan ceritanya.
Translated Text:
The film is shown in black and white which I assume has something to do with Aman being color blind.

To be honest, this movie has its own fans and not everyone can accept the storyline.

Text:
Filem ini banyak tersirat daripada yang tersurat. Maka terpulang kepada kita untuk membuat konklusi. Satu perkara yang saya amat kecewa adalah babak akhir yang tiada klimaks serta penghujung. 

Filem ini terhenti pada saat yang kita perlu jawapan bukan persoalan.
Translated Text:
This movie is more implied than written. So it is up to us to draw conclusions. One thing that I was very disappointed with was the final scene which had no climax and no ending.

The film stops at a moment when we need answers not questions.

Text:
Filem ini mempunyai peminat tersendiri dan bukan semua mampu menerima cara jalan ceritanya. 

Saya puji seni yang dizahirkan namun bukan semua mampu memahami isi yang tersirat. 

Skala:6.5/10
Translated Text:
This film has its own fans and not all are able to accept the way the story is told.

I praise the art expressed but not everyone is able to understand the implied content.

Scale: 6.5/10

Text:
Pembuat keputusan gambar terbaik telah dihakimi oleh warga maya dengan memilih gambar yang cantik di mata. 

Nampaknya telefon pintar kelas pertengahan Google Pixel 5A menjuarai ujian rahsia yang dijalankan oleh MKBHD.
Translated Text:
The decision maker of the best picture was judged by the virtual citizens by choosing a picture that was beautiful to the eye.

It seems that the mid-range smartphone Google Pixel 5A won the secret test conducted by MKBHD.

Text:
Pixel 5A telah menewaskan beberapa model andalan seperti iPhone 13 Pro Max, Samsung Galaxy 21 Ultra, Sony Xperia Pro i dan lain-lain.

Menurut MKBHD, kebanyakan warga maya cenderung untuk memilih gambar yang cerah walaupun ia bukan penanda aras kepada kualiti sesebuah gambar.
Translated Text:
Pixel 5A has beaten several flagship models such as iPhone 13 Pro Max, Samsung Galaxy 21 Ultra, Sony Xperia Pro i and others.

According to MKBHD, most virtual citizens tend to choose bright pictures even though it is not a benchmark for the quality of a picture.

Text: MKBHD juga turut mendapat kritikan disebabkan gambar yang dimuat naik di media sosial telah mengalami penurunan kualiti serta mencacatkan kualiti asal sesebuah gambar.
Translated Text: MKBHD has also received criticism due to the fact that pictures uploaded on social media have experienced a decrease in quality and mutilated the original quality of a picture.

Text: Kendatipun begitu, saya bersetuju dengan pandangan MKBHD bahawa majoriti warga maya menilai sesebuah gambar di media sosial tanpa perlu disimpan di storan awan.
Translated Text: Even so, I agree with MKBHD's view that the majority of virtual citizens evaluate a picture on social media without having to save it in cloud storage.

Text:
Ujian rahsia ini memberi gambaran sebenar kecenderungan seseorang itu memilih gambar terbaik. 

Jika perbandingan dibuat dengan meletakkan jenama atau model telefon pintar yang ditangkap, sudah pasti keputusan akan berat sebelah.
Translated Text:
This secret test gives a true picture of a person's tendency to choose the best picture.

If the comparison is made by placing the brand or model of the captured smartphone, it is certain that the results will be biased.

Text:
Buktinya, beberapa tahun lepas saya ada membuat perbandingan gambar di Facebook Apple User Group (AUG) menggunakan Google Pixel 2 XL dan iPhone XS. 

Saya cuba menguji warga AUG bagaimana mereka menilai sesebuah gambar.
Translated Text:
As proof, a few years ago I did a photo comparison on Facebook Apple User Group (AUG) using Google Pixel 2 XL and iPhone XS.

I tried to test the AUG people how they rate a picture.

Text:
Saya telah memuat naik gambar kanan (Pixel) dan kiri (iPhone) yang hakikat sebenarnya kanan (iPhone) dan kiri (Pixel).

Maka ramailah memuji gambar kiri dengan mengangap gambar tersebut nampak semula jadi, cantik dan lain-lain.
Translated Text:
I have uploaded the right (Pixel) and left (iPhone) pictures which are actually right (iPhone) and left (Pixel).

So many people praise the left picture by saying that it looks natural, beautiful and so on.

Text:
Setelah beberapa jam, saya telah menerangkan hal sebenarnya bahawa gambar yang mereka puji adalah Google Pixel 2 XL dan bukan iPhone XS.

Maka segelintir warga AUG mula marah kepada saya kerana menipu.
Translated Text:
After a few hours, I explained the fact that the picture they were praising was the Google Pixel 2 XL and not the iPhone XS.

So a few AUG people started getting mad at me for cheating.

Text:
Mengapa mereka perlu marah? mereka pilih gambar berkualiti atau sekadar mahu menyokong peranti kesayangan mereka?

Konklusinya, ujian buta lebih menggambarkan kecenderungan seseorang itu menilai kualiti gambar.
Translated Text:
Why should they be angry? they choose quality pictures or just want to support their favorite device?

In conclusion, the blind test better reflects the tendency of a person to judge the quality of a picture.

Text:
Ujian buta secara faktanya tidak menggambarkan dalam konteks dokumentasi yang sebenarnya.

@DxOMark antara satu organisasi yang membuat penilaian secara makmal dengan menggunakan pelbagai alat untuk menguji kualiti.
Translated Text:
Blind testing does not actually reflect the actual documentation context.

@DxOMark is one of the organizations that make laboratory evaluations using various tools to test quality.

Text:
Namun keputusan yang dilaporkan sering menjadi buah mulut warga maya dengan mengangap organisasi tersebut berat sebelah.

Bagi saya, kualiti sesebuah gambar bergantung kepada cara kita menangkapya.
Translated Text:
However, the reported results often become the fruit of the mouth of virtual citizens who perceive the organization as biased.

For me, the quality of a picture depends on how we capture it.

Text:
Sehebat mana telefon pintar tersebut, jika tiada kemahiran maka gambar yang dizahirkan tidak akan menarik.

Cuma, beberapa fitur yang terdapat pada peranti terkini sudah mampu menjana kualiti gambar yang menarik walaupun kita tidak begitu mahir untuk mengangkapnya.
Translated Text:
As good as the smartphone is, if there is no skill then the picture displayed will not be attractive.

It's just that, some features available on the latest devices are already capable of generating interesting picture quality even if we are not very good at capturing them.

Text: Macintosh (Mac) merupakan DNA asal Apple, tidak hairanlah produk Mac sangat berkualiti serta premium. Selain itu, sistem pengendalian macOS juga saya anggap antara yang terbaik  dan stabil berbanding Windows.
Translated Text: Macintosh (Mac) is the original DNA of Apple, no wonder Mac products are very high quality and premium. Also, I consider the macOS operating system to be one of the best and most stable compared to Windows.

Text: Kendatipun begitu, dari segi perisian dan mesra permainan, Windows tetap mendominasi pasaran dan mustahil untuk macOS pada ketika ini untuk bersaing dengan Windows dalam segmen tersebut.
Translated Text: Even so, in terms of software and gaming friendliness, Windows still dominates the market and it is impossible for macOS at this point to compete with Windows in that segment.

Text: Apple wewenang untuk hasil Mac yang terbaik  disebabkan mereka membangunkan perisian dan perkakasan bawah satu bumbung. Malangnya Apple hanya memfokuskan kepada produktiviti seperti suntingan video dan gambar dan tidak cenderung untuk membangunkan spesifikasi khas bagi permainan
Translated Text: Apple is the authority on the best Mac products because they develop software and hardware under one roof. Unfortunately Apple only focuses on productivity such as video and photo editing and does not tend to develop special specifications for games

Text:
Antara sebab saya membeli MacBook Pro 14-inci atas faktor inkarnasi pada MagSafe, tambahan port serta kualiti bahan binaan yang sangat mengagumkan.

MacBook juga antara produk terawal pernah saya miliki suatu ketika dahulu.
Translated Text:
Among the reasons I bought the 14-inch MacBook Pro was the incarnation of MagSafe, the additional ports and the very impressive build quality.

MacBook is also one of the earliest products I ever owned once upon a time.

Text:
MacBook mempunyai jangka hayat yang lama dan tidak hairanlah banyak perisian masih berfungsi dengan baik.

Saya ada berbicara tentang transisi Apple dari X86 ke ARM. Saya pernah nyatakan bahawa proses tersebut akan mengambil masa  bagi memastikan perisian menyokong sepenuhnya
Translated Text:
MacBooks have a long lifespan and it's no wonder many software still work well.

I was talking about Apple's transition from X86 to ARM. I mentioned before that the process will take time to ensure the software is fully supported

Text: Nampaknya kebanyakan perisian utama sudah ke arah ARM, macOS juga tidak mengalami masalah kritikal setelah peralihan ini. Pada awal pelancaran MacBook Pro 13-inci, saya menjangkakan peralihan perisian x86 ke ARM akan mengambil masa tiga hingga empat tahun.
Translated Text: It seems that most of the major software is already towards ARM, macOS also does not suffer critical problems after this transition. At the launch of the 13-inch MacBook Pro, I expected the x86 software transition to ARM to take three to four years.

Text:
Nampaknya peralihan agak cepat dan tersusun. Kebanyakan produk Mac juga sudah ke arah ARM. Kini tinggal iMac 27-inci dan Mac Pro yang belum diperkasakan dengan cip Apple.

Saya menjangkakan tahun 2022 fasa terakhir kepada transisi ke ARM.
Translated Text:
It seems like the transition is pretty quick and organized. Most Mac products are also already towards ARM. Now there are only 27-inch iMacs and Mac Pros that haven't been powered by Apple chips.

I expect the year 2022 to be the last phase to transition to ARM.

Text:
Jika Apple dapat memperkenalkan Mac Pro dengan cip Apple pada tahun hadapan, maka lengkap seluruh produk Apple dengan cip buatan sendiri.

Saya tidak akan memperincikan pengalaman penggunaan macOS memandangkan ramai yang menggunakan sistem pengendalian ini.
Translated Text:
If Apple can introduce a Mac Pro with an Apple chip next year, then complete all Apple products with a home-made chip.

I will not go into detail about the experience of using macOS since many people use this operating system.

Text: Sejujurnya saya tiada sebarang masalah untuk menggunakan macOS, walaupun pada peringkat awal kita perlu memahami beberapa perkara termasuklah sistem fail.
Translated Text: To be honest I don't have any problem to use macOS, although at the initial stage we need to understand some things including the file system.

Text: Saya pilih MacBook Pro 14-inci disebabkan oleh minat, iPhone bagi saya sebuah produk yang biasa. iPhone XS saya masih berfungsi dengan baik dan saya hanya perlu menukar bateri di AASP untuk memastikan prestasi kembali ke normal.
Translated Text: I chose the 14-inch MacBook Pro out of interest, the iPhone for me is a familiar product. My iPhone XS is still working fine and I just need to change the battery at AASP to get performance back to normal.

Text:
Insya-Allah dengan pembelian MacBook Pro 14-inci ini, saya boleh kembangkan bakat saya dalam pencipta kandungan dan membuka sebuah saluran YouTube pada masa hadapan.

SEKADAR PANDANGAN
Translated Text:
God willing with the purchase of this 14-inch MacBook Pro, I can develop my talent as a content creator and open a YouTube channel in the future.

JUST A VIEW

Dalam erti kata mudah Sewon mampu untuk menggodam ingatan seseorang ke dalam mindanya. https://t.co/oSuNVvORV6
Translated Text:
Sewon has succeeded in creating a device that can transfer the memories of the deceased into his brain.

In a simple sense, Sewon is able to hack someone's memory into their mind. https://t.co/oSuNVvORV6

Text:
Walaupun penyelidikan yang dilakukan sangat menarik. Sewon dihalang untuk menggunakan manusia untuk kajian tersebut. 

Namun atas bantuan rakan rapatnya, dia berjaya memperoleh seorang lelaki yang baru sahaja meninggal dunia. https://t.co/pdQNIfJ3xE
Translated Text:
Although the research done is very interesting. Sewon is prohibited from using humans for the study.

But with the help of his close friend, he managed to acquire a man who had just died. https://t.co/pdQNIfJ3xE

Text:
Sewaktu pemindahan minda selesai, Sewon dapat merasakan sesuatu yang tidak kena pada mayat tersebut. 

Sewaktu pulang ke rumah, Sewon didatangi oleh seorang Detektif yang menyiasat tentang  isterinya.
Translated Text:
When the mind transfer was complete, Sewon could sense something was wrong with the corpse.

While returning home, Sewon is approached by a Detective who investigates about his wife.

Text:
Sewon hakikatnya mempunyai seorang Isteri dan anak lelaki. Malangnya anaknya meninggal dunia manakala isterinya koma disebabkan cuba membunuh diri. 

Disebabkan hal tersebut, Sewon sering diganggu oleh Detektif tersebut.
Translated Text:
Sewon actually has a wife and a son. Unfortunately, his son died while his wife was in a coma due to a suicide attempt.

Because of that, Sewon is often harassed by the Detective.

Text:
Sewon yang pada mulanya menjadikan kajiannya untuk penyelidikan menjadi satu medium untuk membongkar kematian anaknya. 

Sewon mendapati terdapat keraguan berkait kematian anaknya. Adakah benar atau hanya igauan?
Translated Text:
Sewon who initially turned his studies for research into a medium to uncover his son's death.

Sewon found that there were doubts about his son's death. Is it true or just a delusion?

Text: Menarik drama Korea ini adalah peranti yang mereka gunakan. Jika sebelum ini Samsung menjadi daya penarik, untuk drama ini produk Apple seperti iPhone dan MacBook ditonjolkan secara dekat.

Text:
Ramai yang salah faham, rangkaian 5G terbahagi kepada dua iaitu Sub-6GHz dan mmWave. 

mmWave merupakan rangkaian terpantas 5G manakala Sub-6GHz sedikit perlahan namun meluas.
Translated Text:
Many people misunderstand, the 5G network is divided into two, namely Sub-6GHz and mmWave.

mmWave is the fastest 5G network while Sub-6GHz is slightly slower but widespread.

Text:
Gambar sebelah kanan yang ditunjukkan oleh individu tersebut adalah mmWave dan setakat ini hanya menyokong di negara Amerika Syarikat. 

Jika di bawa ke Malaysia sekalipun rangkaian tersebut tidak menyokong kecuali mmWave dibangunkan.
Translated Text:
The picture on the right shown by the individual is mmWave and so far only supports in the United States.

Even if brought to Malaysia, the network does not support unless mmWave is developed.

Text: Konklusinya, semua model iPhone 12 dan iPhone 13 di Malaysia menyokong 5G dengan Sub-6GHz.
Translated Text: In conclusion, all iPhone 12 and iPhone 13 models in Malaysia support 5G with Sub-6GHz.

Text:
Jika anda menerima notifikasi seperti di atas berkemungkinan:

1. Alat ganti tiruan
2. Telah digunakan atau dipasang dalam iPhone lain
3. Tidak berfungsi dengan baik
Translated Text:
If you receive a notification like the above it is possible:

1. Counterfeit parts
2. Has been used or installed in another iPhone
3. Not working properly

Text:
Jika anda menerima notifikasi sedemikian, sila berhubung dengan kedai yang anda baik pulih untuk dapatkan penjelasan lanjut.

Perlu diingatkan, penjelasan tersebut hanya terpakai jika Penjual bermati-matian mengatakan bahawa alat ganti mereka asli.

It should be noted, the explanation only applies if the Seller insists that their parts are genuine.

Text: Jika mereka tidak menyatakan tentang status alat ganti sewaktu membaiki iPhone anda. Maka anda tidak boleh menyalahkan Penjual jika mereka menggunakan alat ganti tiruan.

Text: Jika stok ada dan boleh buat pembelian, minta mereka beri penjelasan mengapa Apple Watch anda masih belum sampai sedangkan mereka sudah menjual tanpa perlu membuat pra-pesanan.
Translated Text: If the stock is available and you can make a purchase, ask them to explain why your Apple Watch has not yet arrived when they have already sold without the need to pre-order.

Text:
Jika hal ini berlaku kepada saya, rasanya boleh bergegar AAR di situ.

Keutamaan diberikan kepada orang yang telah membuat pra-pesanan. Mengapa mereka boleh jual tanpa utamakan orang yang buat tempahan lebih awal.
Translated Text:
If this happens to me, it feels like shaking AAR right there.

Priority is given to people who have pre-ordered. Why can they sell without prioritizing people who made reservations in advance.

Text:
Jika kes ini berlaku kepada anda, sila nyatakan AAR tersebut. Kita sama-sama boikot dan minta mereka beri penjelasan.

Perlu diingatkan, kenyataan yang saya buat ini berkait dengan isu yang saya nyatakan di atas.

If this case happens to you, please mention the AAR. We both boycott and ask them to explain.

It should be noted that the statement I made is related to the issue I mentioned above.

In addition, there are still many stores that have not yet opened, based on my observations most of the stores will open around January to March 2022.

Text:
Dari segi kosmetik dan tandas, saya lebih menyukai @Sunway_Pyramid berbanding Pavilion Bukit Jalil.

Secara keseluruhan, Pavilion Bukit Jalil belum dibuka sepenuhnya. Jika sekadar untuk bersiar, bagi saya tiada masalah.
Translated Text:
In terms of cosmetics and toilets, I like @Sunway_Pyramid better than Bukit Jalil Pavilion.

Overall, Bukit Jalil Pavilion has not been fully opened. If it's just for sightseeing, for me there is no problem.

Text:
Jika anda berharap banyak kedai di sana dibuka, mungkin sangkaan anda meleset.

Banyak yang menarik di Pavilion Bukit Jalil, cuma perlu menunggu sehingga Mac 2022 untuk merasai sepenuhnya pengalaman membeli belah.
Translated Text:
If you were hoping that many stores there would be open, you might be wrong.

There's a lot to enjoy at Bukit Jalil Pavilion, just have to wait until March 2022 to fully enjoy the shopping experience.

Text: Walakin begitu, saya lihat kita terlalu banyak gedung membeli belah. Tropicana Gardens Mall yang dibuka sejak tahun lepas masih suram disebabkan masih banyak kedai yang belum dibuka.
Translated Text: However, I see we have too many department stores. Tropicana Gardens Mall, which opened last year, is still gloomy because there are still many stores that have not yet opened.

Text:
Strand Mall, Space U8 menanti masa untuk rebah. Saya percaya keadaan seperti ini sangat tidak baik untuk ekonomi negara kita.

Kita terlalu banyak gedung membeli belah, sedangkan kuasa beli rakyat tidaklah setinggi gunung.
Translated Text:
Strand Mall, Space U8 waiting for time to collapse. I believe this kind of situation is very bad for our country's economy.

We have too many shopping malls, while the purchasing power of the people is not as high as a mountain.

Text:

Text:
Saya percaya fitur ini bakal menjadi mimpi ngeri bagi segelintir Penjual yang sebelum ini bermati-matian mengatakan alat ganti mereka asli.

Secara fakta, Apple hanya memberi akses kepada alat ganti asli di Pusat Servis yang sah sahaja.
Translated Text:
I believe this feature is going to be a nightmare for a few Sellers who have previously been desperate to say their parts are original.

In fact, Apple only gives access to original spare parts at authorized Service Centers.

Text:
Walakin begitu, terdapat segelintir Penjual  mengatakan alat ganti mereka asli dan diperoleh daripada "pintu belakang".

Saya tidak katakan tiada alat ganti asli di luar sana. Cuma amat mustahil untuk diperoleh dengan mudah.
Translated Text:
However, there are quite a few Sellers who say their parts are genuine and obtained from the "back door".

I'm not saying there aren't genuine parts out there. It's just impossible to get easily.

Text:
Kebiasaannya segelintir Penjual melarang Pengguna untuk mengemaskini iOS.

Mereka memberi alasan pepijat punca kepada masalah pada alat ganti terutama bateri, panel skrin dan lain-lain.
Translated Text:
Usually some Vendors forbid Users to update iOS.

They give the reason that the bug is caused by problems with spare parts, especially batteries, screen panels and others.

Text:
Isu ini bukanlah baharu. Sebelum ini aksesori seperti kabel lightning serta earpod yang kononnya asli banyak dijual di pasaran.

Selepas kemas kini iOS, secara tiba-tiba aksesori tersebut gagal berfungsi atau terdapat notifikasi menunjukkan aksesori tersebut tiruan.
Translated Text:
This issue is not new. Previously, accessories such as lightning cables and earpods that were supposedly original were widely sold in the market.

After the iOS update, suddenly the accessory fails to work or there is a notification indicating that the accessory is fake.

Text:
Seperti biasa, segelintir Penjual akan menyalahkan iOS walhal aksesori yang mereka jual adalah tiruan.

Saya akui pepijat pada iOS boleh dijadikan sebagai punca. Namun janganlah letakkan semua yang berlaku disebabkan oleh iOS.
Translated Text:
As always, some Sellers will blame iOS as the accessories they sell are fake.

I admit a bug in iOS could be the cause. But don't put everything that happens because of iOS.

Text:
Bagi kes pembelian iPhone terpakai, jika Penjual mengatakan iPhone tersebut asli luar dan dalam

Saya galakkan anda untuk hantar ke AASP untuk diagnostik bagi mengesahkan keaslian tersebut. Jika AASP mengesahkan ia tiruan, anda boleh buat tuntutan dengan kedai terbabit
Translated Text:
For the case of buying a used iPhone, if the Seller says the iPhone is original inside and out

I encourage you to send it to AASP for diagnostics to confirm its authenticity. If AASP confirms it is fake, you can make a claim with the store involved

Text: Namun, jika Penjual tidak menyebut tentang keaslian iPhone tersebut. Maka anda tidak boleh salahkan Penjual memandangkan iPhone terpakai semestinya mempunyai masalah dalam menentukan keaslian alat ganti.
Translated Text: However, if the Seller does not mention the authenticity of the iPhone. Then you can't blame the Seller since used iPhones must have problems in determining the authenticity of spare parts.

Text:
Berbalik kepada fitur baharu pada iOS 15.2. Anda boleh membuat verifikasi sama ada alat ganti yang ditukar benar-benar asli atau sebaliknya.

Kendatipun begitu, bagi iPhone XR, iPhone XS, iPhone XS Max serta iPhone SE (2020) hanya status keaslian bateri sahaja yang dipaparkan. https://t.co/8F7w1gHnwJ
Translated Text:
Back to the new features in iOS 15.2. You can verify whether the replacement part is really original or vice versa.

Even so, for iPhone XR, iPhone XS, iPhone XS Max and iPhone SE (2020) only the status of battery authenticity is displayed. https://t.co/8F7w1gHnwJ

Text:
Bagi iPhone 11, iPhone 11 Pro dan iPhone 11 Pro Max, iOS 15.2 dapat mengesahkan status keaslian bagi bateri dan skrin.

Untuk semua model iPhone 12 dan iPhone 13, iOS 15.2 dapat membuat verifikasi pada alat ganti bateri, skrin serta kamera. https://t.co/b3GtDyVsRe
Translated Text:
For iPhone 11, iPhone 11 Pro and iPhone 11 Pro Max, iOS 15.2 can verify the original status for the battery and screen.

For all iPhone 12 and iPhone 13 models, iOS 15.2 can verify battery, screen and camera replacement devices. https://t.co/b3GtDyVsRe

Text:
Konklusinya, iOS 15.2 sedikit sebanyak dapat membongkar penipuan yang dibuat oleh segelintir Penjual.

Hakikatnya, kita digalakkan untuk menghantar iPhone ke AASP untuk penukaran bateri, skrin serta kamera.
Translated Text:
In conclusion, iOS 15.2 can to some extent uncover the fraud made by a few Sellers.

In fact, we are encouraged to send iPhones to AASP for battery, screen and camera replacement.

Text:
Hanya AASP yang mampu menawarkan alat ganti asli kepada semua.

Perlu diingatkan, sekiranya anda menghantar iPhone ke kedai biasa untuk dibaiki atau penukaran bateri dan lain-lain. Sekiranya Apple membuka program khusus untuk iPhone tersebut dan iPhone anda terlibat.
Translated Text:
Only AASP is able to offer genuine spare parts to all.

It should be noted, if you send the iPhone to a regular store for repair or battery replacement etc. If Apple opens a specific program for that iPhone and your iPhone is involved.

Text:
Kebarangkalian AASP menolak permohonan anda adalah tinggi disebabkan pernah membaiki selain AASP.

Saya menjangkakan iOS 15.2 dilancarkan seawal pagi rabu minggu depan.

SEKADAR PANDANGAN

Text:
Kedatangan pengunjung ke Program 100 Hari Aspirasi Keluarga Malaysia boleh menjadi bom jangka yang akan meletus virus Covid-19 dengan lebih parah.

Bila kes meningkat kembali, sudah pasti rakyat yang disalahkan. Adakah mereka sedar bahawa punca masalah datangnya daripada mereka.

The arrival of visitors to the 100 Days of Malaysian Family Aspirations Program can be a time bomb that will explode the Covid-19 virus more severely.

When cases increase again, it is certain that the people are to blame. Do they realize that the cause of the problem comes from them.

Text:
Siapa mereka? 

Sekuat besi kersani, lebih keras jemala mereka. Sombong, bongkak dan hilang hormat pada rakyat jelata. 

Rakyat sudah musnah kesan kebejatan melanda. Mereka harus bersyukur rakyat tidak menghunus keris tertusuk jantung.
Translated Text:
Who are they?

As strong as the iron of art, they are even harder. Arrogant, arrogant and disrespectful to the common people.

The people have been destroyed by the effects of corruption. They should be grateful that the people did not draw a dagger through the heart.

Text:
Menurut Ming-Chi Kuo, iPhone SE 3 masih menggunakan reka bentuk daripada iPhone SE (2020) namun diperkasakan dengan cip A15 Bionic serta sokongan 5G. 

Ini bermakna, iPhone SE 3 kekal dengan saiz 4.7-inci dan Touch ID.
Translated Text:
According to Ming-Chi Kuo, the iPhone SE 3 still uses the design of the iPhone SE (2020) but is powered by an A15 Bionic chip and 5G support.

This means, iPhone SE 3 remains with 4.7-inch size and Touch ID.

Text:
Saya menjangkakan iPhone SE 3 dilancarkan seawal April 2022 dengan tanda harga RM1,999 bagi storan 128GB. 

Saya kurang mempercayai maklumat yang dilaporkan oleh DigiTimes.
Translated Text:
I expect the iPhone SE 3 to be launched as early as April 2022 with a price tag of RM1,999 for 128GB storage.

I have little faith in the information reported by DigiTimes.

Text: Memandangkan laporan tersebut tidak kontradiksi dengan Ming-Chi Kuo serta The Elec, maka untuk maklumat ini saya menerimanya dan berkongsi kepada anda semua.
Translated Text: Since the report does not contradict Ming-Chi Kuo and The Elec, then for this information I accept it and share it with you all.

Text:
Saya akui ramai yang tidak berpuas hati dengan tindakan Apple mengekalkan bentuk iPhone SE.  

Perlu diingatkan, jika Apple menggunakan reka bentuk iPhone XR serta menggunakan cip A15 Bionic. 

Bagaimana nasib iPhone 11?
Translated Text:
I admit that many people are not happy with Apple's actions to maintain the shape of the iPhone SE.

It should be noted, if Apple uses the iPhone XR design and uses the A15 Bionic chip.

What is the fate of the iPhone 11?

Text:
Saya pernah menjelaskan bahawa iPhone SE adalah pek permulaan bagi pengguna Android yang ingin merasai pengalaman menggunakan iOS. 

Selain itu, pengguna iPhone 6 dan iPhone 6 Plus ke bawah mungkin menjadikan iPhone SE sebagai transisi mereka atas faktor harga.
Translated Text:

Text:

Kes ini juga termasuklah penggunaan pelindung pada papan kekunci.
Translated Text:
The use of accessories such as frames or MacBook cases has the potential to cause interference with the ventilation system.

This case also includes the use of a protector on the keyboard.

Text:
Kendatipun begitu, terpulang kepada kebijaksanaan individu tersebut menjaga MacBook. 

Namun bagi saya, penggunaan aksesori lebih beri mudarat dari kebaikan.
Translated Text:
However, it is up to the discretion of the individual to take care of the MacBook.

But for me, the use of accessories does more harm than good.

Text:

It is certain that this year no new products will be launched by Apple.

Text:
Menjadi kebiasaan produk terkini akan lebih baik berbanding model terdahulu.

Saya sering menerima soalan berhubung perbandingan antara model lama dan akan datang, manakah paling berbaloi.
Translated Text:
Get used to the latest product being better than the previous model.

I often receive questions regarding the comparison between the old and upcoming models, which is the best value.

Text:
Sejujurnya mereka sendiri sudah ketahui jawapannya. Namun sudah menjadi lumrah seseorang itu bertanya soalan yang dia sendiri tahu jawapannya. 

Berbalik kepada topik asal, adakah AirPods Pro berbaloi untuk dibeli pada ketika ini?

To be honest, they themselves already know the answer. But it is natural for a person to ask a question that he himself knows the answer to.

Back to the original topic, are AirPods Pro worth buying at this point?

Text:
Apabila soalan ini dikemukakan, perlu diingatkan bahawa tiada tarikh atau bulan yang spesifik untuk pelancaran AirPods Pro. 

AirPods Pro sebelum ini dilancarkan pada bulan Oktober 2019 dan sehingga kini tiada naik taraf baharu.
Translated Text:
When this question is asked, it should be noted that there is no specific date or month for the launch of AirPods Pro.

AirPods Pro was previously launched in October 2019 and until now there are no new upgrades.

Text:
Terkini, satu sumber yang boleh dipercayai telah dilaporkan oleh Ming-Chi Kuo yang mengatakan bahawa AirPods Pro 2 bakal dilancarkan pada suku keempat tahun hadapan. 

AirPods Pro 2 dikhabarkan akan hadir dengan reka bentuk baharu serta naik taraf cip yang lebih baik.
Translated Text:
Recently, a reliable source has been reported by Ming-Chi Kuo who says that AirPods Pro 2 will be launched in the fourth quarter of next year.

AirPods Pro 2 is rumored to come with a new design as well as a better chip upgrade.

Text:
Ini bermakna, kita perlu menunggu hampir setahun lagi untuk melihat AirPods Pro terbaharu. 

Maka wajarlah untuk beli AirPods Pro pada waktu ini. AirPods Pro juga telah dijual pada harga RM899 di beberapa AAR yang bagi saya sangat berbaloi.
Translated Text:
This means, we have to wait almost another year to see the latest AirPods Pro.

So it makes sense to buy AirPods Pro at this time. AirPods Pro has also been sold at a price of RM899 in some AARs which for me is very worthwhile.

Text:
Harga rasmi AirPods Pro adalah RM1,099. Maka rebut peluang untuk membeli AirPods Pro pada harga diskaun. 

Konklusinya, apabila mempersoalkan kewajaran membeli AirPods Pro sekarang atau akan datang.
Translated Text:
The official price of AirPods Pro is RM1,099. So grab the opportunity to buy AirPods Pro at a discounted price.

The conclusion, when questioning the propriety of buying AirPods Pro now or in the future.

Text:
Lihat kepada keinginan kita sama ada mahukan sekarang atau akan datang. 

AirPods Pro 2 mungkin dilancarkan pada lewat tahun 2022 yang bagi saya terlalu lama untuk ditunggu.
Translated Text:
Look at our desires whether we want now or in the future.

AirPods Pro 2 may launch in late 2022 which for me is too long to wait.

Text:
Jika anda sanggup menunggu, hakikatnya AirPods Pro bukan keperluan anda pada waktu ini. 

Jika anda mahu beli sekarang, bagi saya tiada masalah dan paling penting beli di AAR, LazMall atau Shopee Mall.
Translated Text:
If you are willing to wait, the fact is that AirPods Pro are not what you need at this time.

If you want to buy now, for me there is no problem and most importantly buy at AAR, LazMall or Shopee Mall.

Text:
Saya kurang menggalakkan anda beli di kedai biasa, Instagram, orang persendirian atau laman jual beli yang tidak menepati piawaian. 

Kendatipun begitu, saya tidak katakan laporan daripada Ming-Chi Kuo tepat, tapi saya mempercayainya.
Translated Text:
I don't encourage you to buy from regular stores, Instagram, private people or buying and selling sites that don't meet the standards.

Even so, I'm not saying the report from Ming-Chi Kuo is accurate, but I believe it.

Text: Kendatipun begitu, saya berpandangan masih terlalu awal Pixel Watch untuk menandingi Apple Watch memandangkan Apple Watch mempunyai banyak keistimewaan yang menyebabkan  pengguna mahu memilikinya.

Text:
Walaupun kejuruteraan perisian dan perkakasan di bawah satu bumbung, Pixel Watch masih dalam fasa percubaan untuk memasuki pasaran jam pintar.

Jika dilihat Apple sangat komitmen dalam membangunkan Apple Watch.

Despite software and hardware engineering under one roof, the Pixel Watch is still in the experimental phase of entering the smartwatch market.

Text:

Saya akui Pixel Phone mungkin menjadi pencabar iPhone namun tidak bagi Pixel Watch bersaing dengan Apple Watch.

Text:

Google perlu hasilkan fitur yang menarik jika mahu kekal relevan dalam pasaran.

Text:

Text:
Rakan saya juga telah menerima nasihat saya untuk melanggan pelan SPP Lite selama setahun dengan bayaran RM129.

Ini bermakna jumlah bayaran yang dikenakan adalah sebanyak RM1,428. Kendatipun begitu, bayaran pertama dikenakan hanyalah RM476 sahaja.
Translated Text:
My friend has also accepted my advice to subscribe to the SPP Lite plan for a year for RM129.

This means that the total fee charged is RM1,428. Even so, the first payment is only RM476.

Text:
Selebihnya akan ditolak pada bulan Januari (RM476) dan Februari (RM476) tahun hadapan.

Sebab utama saya menggalakkan untuk mengambil SPP Lite daripada @SwitchTM atas faktor keselamatan.
Translated Text:
The rest will be deducted in January (RM476) and February (RM476) next year.

The main reason I encourage to take SPP Lite from @SwitchTM is security factor.

Text:
Jika Apple Watch pecah atau rosak disebabkan masuk air, kita hanya perlu membayar RM180 sahaja untuk mendapatkan set gantian baharu.

Selain itu, saya turut cenderung agar dia memilih edisi Nike atas faktor tambahan muka jam, kosmetik serta susut nilai yang rendah.
Translated Text:
If the Apple Watch breaks or is damaged due to water, we only need to pay RM180 to get a new replacement set.

In addition, I am also inclined to have him choose the Nike edition due to the additional factors of the face, cosmetics and low depreciation.

Text:
Saya tidak menggalakkan rakan saya mengambil versi GPS+Selular disebabkan tambahan kos langganan daripada syarikat telekomunikasi.

Konklusinya, saya menggalakkan anda untuk beli Apple Watch SE atau Siri 7 edisi Nike berbanding biasa.
Translated Text:
I do not encourage my friends to take the GPS+Cellular version due to the additional subscription cost from the telco.

In conclusion, I encourage you to buy the Nike edition Apple Watch SE or Series 7 over the regular one.

Text:
Mohon langgan skim pelindungan seperti SPP Lite, MPP serta setaraf dan jika tidak mahu tambahan kepada kos, beli sahaja versi GPS.

Saya puji hospitaliti yang ditunjukkan oleh kakitangan @SwitchTM Sunway Pyramid. Kekalkan momentum dan terus layan pelanggan anda sebaik-baiknya.
Translated Text:
Please subscribe to protection schemes such as SPP Lite, MPP and equivalent and if you don't want to add to the cost, just buy the GPS version.

I commend the hospitality shown by @SwitchTM Sunway Pyramid staff. Keep up the momentum and continue to serve your customers the best.

Text:

They introduced e-wallet but it was only accepted at some toll plazas.

Text:

Sebelum ini saya telah mengeluarkan satu rajutan (thread) tentang sindiket penipuan penjualan AirPods Pro tiruan.
Translated Text:
What lessons can be used as a guide?

Previously I have released a thread about a fraudulent syndicate selling fake AirPods Pro.

Text:
Dalam rajutan tersebut, telah diperincikan modus operandi serta sifat AirPods Pro tiruan tersebut. 

Seperti yang saya nyatakan sebelum ini. Jika kita belum mahir tentang selok belok pembelian AirPods Pro. Sila beli di AAR sahaja.
Translated Text:
In the knitting, the modus operandi and properties of the fake AirPods Pro have been detailed.

As I mentioned before. If we are not yet well versed in the ins and outs of purchasing AirPods Pro. Please buy at AAR only.

Text: AirPods Pro pada ketika ini dijual pada harga RM899 di AAR. Mohon beli di AAR dan elak untuk membeli di saluran yang tidak sah seperti Instagram dan lain-lain.
Translated Text: AirPods Pro is currently sold at a price of RM899 at AAR. Please buy on AAR and avoid buying on illegal channels like Instagram and others.

Text:
Tiada masalah untuk beli di Lazada atau Shopee tapi wajib beli di kedai yang berstatus LazMall atau Shopee Mall. 

Perlu diingatkan bateri AirPods Pro tidak boleh ditukar di AASP. Sifat bateri mempunyai jangka hayat.
Translated Text:
There is no problem to buy at Lazada or Shopee but it is mandatory to buy at a store with LazMall or Shopee Mall status.

It should be noted that AirPods Pro batteries are not replaceable at AASP. Battery properties have a lifespan.

Text:
Saya meramalkan jangka hayat AirPods Pro sekitar dua tahun jika digunakan secara kerap. 

Oleh itu, digalakkan untuk beli AirPods Pro baharu dan jauhi yang terpakai.
Translated Text:
I predict an AirPods Pro lifespan of around two years with regular use.

Therefore, it is recommended to buy new AirPods Pro and stay away from used ones.

Text:
AirPods Pro amat sukar untuk dibezakan yang asli atau tiruan memandangkan kilang di sana sudah mampu untuk jiplak seakan asli. 

Saya pernah berkongsi perbezaan AirPods Pro tiruan dan asli.
Translated Text:
AirPods Pro is very difficult to distinguish the original or counterfeit since the factory there is already capable of counterfeiting as if it were original.

I have shared the difference between fake and original AirPods Pro.

Text: Kendatipun begitu, saya telah jelaskan bahawa AirPods Pro tiruan akan mengalami fasa evolusi yang pantas dan mereka mampu untuk menyelesaikan kelemahan yang terdapat pada AirPods Pro tiruan versi sebelum ini.
Translated Text: Nevertheless, I have already explained that the fake AirPods Pro will undergo a rapid evolution phase and they will be able to solve the weaknesses found in the previous versions of the fake AirPods Pro.

Text:
Konklusinya, sememangnya terdapat panduan untuk membezakan antara tiruan dan asli. 

Walakin begitu, saya lebih menggalakkan anda untuk terus beli di AAR berbanding menjadi Detektif Conan.
Translated Text:
In conclusion, there is indeed a guide to distinguish between imitation and original.

However, I encourage you to continue shopping at AAR rather than becoming Detective Conan.

Text:
Ingat pesanan saya, AirPods Pro tiruan akan mengalami fasa evolusi yang pantas. 

Mereka wewenang untuk menyelesaikan kelemahan yang ada pada AirPods Pro tiruan sebelum ini.
Translated Text:
Remember my order, clone AirPods Pro will undergo a proper evolutionary phase.

They are authorized to solve the weaknesses that existed in previous AirPods Pro clones.

Text:
@AmirHannnnnnnn Sebab unit saham lebih besar. 

Contohnya 100 unit bagi RM1 (RM100), jika waktu itu pasaran turun RM0.50 kita tambah pelaburan, kita akan peroleh 200 unit (RM100)

Jika pasaran naik RM1.50 maka kita dapat, RM1.50 x 300 unit = RM450. 

Ini contoh sahaja, untuk mudahkan pemahaman.
Translated Text:
@AmirHannnnnnnn Because the stock unit is bigger.

For example 100 units for RM1 (RM100), if at that time the market goes down RM0.50 we add investment, we will get 200 units (RM100)

If the market goes up by RM1.50 then we get, RM1.50 x 300 units = RM450.

This is just an example, to make it easier to understand.

Text:
Apple dijangka akan menyenaraikan iPhone 6 Plus sebagai produk vintaj pada 31 Disember 2021. 

Ini bermakna iPhone 6 dan iPhone 5s mungkin akan tersenarai bersama iPhone 6 Plus.

Apple is expected to list the iPhone 6 Plus as a vintage product on December 31, 2021.

This means the iPhone 6 and iPhone 5s will likely be listed alongside the iPhone 6 Plus.

Text:
Untuk makluman semua, iPhone 6 dan iPhone 6 Plus merupakan satu-satunya telefon pintar yang berjaya mencecah jualan sehingga 220 juta. 

Tiada satu jenama dalam dunia ini mampu sampai ke tahap tersebut.
Translated Text:
For everyone's information, the iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus are the only smartphones that managed to reach sales of up to 220 million.

No other brand in the world can reach that level.

Text:
Kendatipun begitu, Nokia 1100 kekal sebagai telefon bimbit tertinggi dari segi jualan iaitu sebanyak 250 juta unit. 

iPhone 6 dan iPhone 6 Plus merupakan model pertama hadir dengan dua saiz serta sokongan Apple Pay. https://t.co/Tlxw59siZ3
Translated Text:
Despite that, the Nokia 1100 remains the highest mobile phone in terms of sales, which is 250 million units.

The iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus are the first models to come in two sizes and support Apple Pay. https://t.co/Tlxw59siZ3

Text:

Text:
Saya faham situasi saudara yang belum biasa dengan macOS.

Transisi Windows ke macOS memerlukan sedikit masa memandangkan cara pengendalian sangat berbeza.
Translated Text:
I understand the situation of those who are not familiar with macOS.

The Windows to macOS transition will take some time as the operating methods are very different.

Text:
Antara muka pengguna serta pengalaman penggunaan sangatlah berbeza. 

Saudara memerlukan sedikit masa untuk memahirkan diri dalam menggunakan macOS.
Translated Text:
The user interface and user experience are very different.

You need some time to get used to using macOS.

Text:
Antara keluhan yang sering saya terima:

1- Sambungan cakera keras luaran (external hard disk) 
2- Pemasangan perisian 
3- Sokongan perisian 
4- Pengurusan data
5- lain-lain
Translated Text:
Among the complaints I often receive:

1- External hard disk connection (external hard disk)
2- Software installation
3- Software support
4- Data management
5- others

Text:
Saya galakkan saudara untuk berlatih untuk tempoh satu hingga dua bulan dan memahami sedikit sebanyak tatacara pengendalian macOS. 

Sejujurnya cara menggunakan macOS jauh lebih baik berbanding Windows.
Translated Text:
I encourage you to practice for a period of one to two months and understand a little about the macOS operating system.

To be honest, using macOS is much better than Windows.

Text:
Kendatipun begitu, saya mengakui macOS tidak mesra permainan.  

Namun bagi tujuan selain daripada itu, bagi saya sangat produktif terutama jika kita mempunyai iPhone, iPad dan lain-lain.
Translated Text:
Even so, I admit macOS is not gaming friendly.

But for purposes other than that, for me it is very productive especially if we have an iPhone, iPad and others.

Text:
Saya berharap saudara berlatih dahulu. Saya akui cara pengendalian sangat berbeza. 

Namun saay kita guna macOS, kita tidak akan toleh ke belakang.
Translated Text:
I hope you practice first. I admit the handling is very different.

But if we use macOS, we won't look back.

If adding an investment AFTER 12.00 noon business time, funds will be invested according to the market closing price of the next business day.

However, if the investment is added it is not a business day.

Text:
Saya kurang menggalakkan penggunaan pelindung lensa bagi mengelakkan masalah kosmetik terutama pada iPhone XR, iPhone 11, iPhone 12 dan iPhone 13. 

Aksesori ini juga berpotensi mengganggu kualiti gambar yang ditangkap. Namun tiada masalah untuk memakainya atas faktor keselamatan
Translated Text:
I do not encourage the use of lens protectors to avoid cosmetic problems, especially on the iPhone XR, iPhone 11, iPhone 12 and iPhone 13.

These accessories also have the potential to interfere with the quality of captured images. But there is no problem to wear it for safety reasons

Text: Saya tidak meletakkan sebarang standard khusus bagi aksesori ini. Tanggungjawab kita sebagai pengguna untuk memilih aksesori yang sesuai.

Kerana itulah saya tidak pertikai tentang harga MacBook tersebut.

MacBook Pro 14-inci dan 16-inci berada dalam kategori baharu dan tidak dipastikan nasib MacBook Pro 13-inci. Adakah MacBook Pro dianggap iPhone 13 manakala MacBook Air iPhone 13 mini kita lihat nanti

Text:
Sebelum pelancaran MacBook Pro 14-inci, saya tidak mengharapkan sesuatu yang menarik. Kerana:

"Apple tetap Apple" 

Berbeza dengan zaman Steve Jobs, saya menantikan apakah inovasi yang bakal dihidangkan kepada kita semua.
Translated Text:
Before the launch of the 14-inch MacBook Pro, I did not expect anything exciting. Because:

"Apple is still Apple"

Unlike the days of Steve Jobs, I look forward to what innovations will be served to all of us.

Text:
Namun sewaktu Acara pelancaran MacBook, saya terdiam dan terus jatuh cinta pada MacBook Pro 14-inci.

Bukan kerana cip M1 Pro atau Max semata-mata. Namun inkarnasi yang dibuat oleh Apple pada MacBook.
Translated Text:
But during the MacBook launch event, I fell silent and fell in love with the 14-inch MacBook Pro.

Not because of the M1 Pro or Max chip alone. Yet the incarnation made by Apple on the MacBook.

Text:
Terlalu banyak inovasi yang diperkenalkan oleh Apple pada MacBook Pro 14-inci.

Saya boleh anggap MacBook Pro 14-inci pembuka lembaran baharu bagi penciptaan MacBook terutama cip pemprosesan berteraskan ARM.
Translated Text:
There are too many innovations introduced by Apple on the 14-inch MacBook Pro.

I can consider the 14-inch MacBook Pro to open a new page for the creation of MacBooks, especially ARM-based processing chips.

Text:
Walaupun saya sudah mempunyai beberapa buah MacBook. Namun MacBook Pro 14-inci berjaya membuatkan saya jatuh cinta.

Saya pernah nyatakan dahulu bahawa saya antara peminat fanatik Apple. Saya sanggup ikat perut untuk mendapatkan produk yang saya hajati.
Translated Text:
Although I already have several MacBooks. But the 14-inch MacBook Pro managed to make me fall in love.

I've mentioned before that I'm an Apple fanatic. I am willing to tie my stomach to get the product I want.

Text:
Walakin begitu, sejak beberapa tahun kebelakangan ini, saya lebih melihat Apple ke arah mengejar keuntungan terutama pada penciptaan iPhone dan Mac.

Sejak tercetus cip pemprosesan buatan Apple sendiri. Apple telah merubah perkembangan MacBook.
Translated Text:
However, over the past few years, I have seen Apple more towards the pursuit of profits, especially in the creation of the iPhone and Mac.

Since the emergence of Apple's own processing chips. Apple has changed the development of the MacBook.

Text:
MacBook masih kekal dengan DNA asal. Cuma saya mempunyai beberapa sebab mengapa saya sanggup membeli MacBook Pro 14-inci.

Wang tabungan yang saya simpan untuk iPhone 13 Pro Max telah beralih ke MacBook Pro 14-inci
Translated Text:
MacBook still remains with the original DNA. It's just that I have a few reasons why I'm willing to buy a 14-inch MacBook Pro.

The savings I saved for the iPhone 13 Pro Max have gone to the 14-inch MacBook Pro

Text:
Ya, saya akan beli. Bukan kerana taksub dengan prestasi MacBook Pro semata-mata. Namun terdapat beberapa sebab lain yang akan saya kongsi.

Saya tidak terlalu teruja dengan iPhone sejak beberapa tahun kebelakangan ini.
Translated Text:
Yes, I will buy it. Not because of obsession with MacBook Pro performance alone. But there are some other reasons that I will share.

I haven't been too excited about iPhones in recent years.

Text:
Saya mahukan sesuatu yang baharu dan segar dan bukan sekadar tangkap muat.

Saya akui MacBook Pro 14-inci banyak mengembalikan sesuatu yang Apple buang suatu ketika dahulu terutama port dan MagSafe.
Translated Text:
I wanted something new and fresh and not just a catch-all.

I admit that the 14-inch MacBook Pro brings back a lot of things that Apple threw away a while ago, especially ports and MagSafe.

Text:
Mereka buat masalah dan mereka cipta penyelesaian semata-mata untuk menarik minat pengguna.

Saya akui semua itu. Hakikatnya ia belum cukup kuat untuk tidak membelinya.
Translated Text:
They create problems and they create solutions simply to attract users.

I admit all that. The fact is that it is not strong enough not to buy it.

Text:
Saya akan cuba membuat tempahan di @SwitchTM.

Saya akan kongsi mengapa dan kenapa membeli MacBook Pro 14-inci berbanding iPhone 13 Pro Max.

Cinta perlukan pengorbanan, namun jika kita mempunyai pilihan yang lebih baik, maka teruskan dan jangan toleh belakang.
Translated Text:
I will try to book on @SwitchTM.

I'll share the whys and wherefores of buying the 14-inch MacBook Pro over the iPhone 13 Pro Max.

Love requires sacrifice, but if we have a better option, then go ahead and don't look back.

Text:
Madeleine Swann mempunyai kehidupan yang penuh rahsia. Sewaktu berbulan madu, satu kumpulan penjenayah telah cuba untuk membunuh James Bond dan kekasihnya.

James Bond mula rasa curiga dengan kekasihnya dan akhirnya mereka terpisah.
Translated Text:
Madeleine Swann has a secret life. During the honeymoon, a group of criminals tried to kill James Bond and his lover.

James Bond became suspicious of his lover and eventually they separated.

Text:
Setelah lima tahun berlalu, satu siri penculikan telah berlaku dan penjenayah yang sama cuba membunuh James Bond telah menculik seorang Saintis iaitu Valdo Obruche.

Valdo Obruche mempunyai maklumat tentang projek Heracles yang berkait dengan senjata biologi.
Translated Text:
After five years have passed, a series of kidnappings have taken place and the same criminals who tried to kill James Bond have kidnapped a Scientist, Valdo Obruche.

Valdo Obruche has information about the Heracles project related to biological weapons.

Text:
Siapa penjenayah terbabit dan apakan kaitan dengan Madeleine Swann . Semuanya akan terjawab setelah anda menontonnya.

Sejujurnya jalan cerita bagi saya biasa sahaja dan yang pasti kita perlu menerima segala logik akal bagi filem ini.
Translated Text:
Who are the criminals involved and what is the connection with Madeleine Swann. Everything will be answered after you watch it.

To be honest, the story line is normal for me and we definitely have to accept all logic for this movie.

Text:
Seperti biasa berpuluh tembakan tidak akan mengenai badan James Bond seolah-olah dia merupakan individu yang "kalis peluru".

Pada babak akhir sedikit lemah terutama sewaktu ketua penjenayah hanya meninggalkan budak perempuan begitu sahaja.
Translated Text:
As usual dozens of shots will not hit the body of James Bond as if he is a "bulletproof" individual.

The final scene was a bit weak, especially when the criminal leader just left the girl alone.

Text:
Cerita ini lebih kepada pengorbanan kasih sayang seorang kekasih dan melangkaui peperangan dunia.

Saya tidak mempertikai jalan cerita James Bond memandangkan ia lebih kurang sahaja dengan filem terdahulu.
Translated Text:
This story is more about the sacrifice of a lover's love and goes beyond world wars.

I'm not disputing the James Bond storyline since it's more or less the same as the previous films.

Text:
Babak akhir James Bond mungkin membuatkan anda menitis air mata dan saya tidak akan menyatakan mengapa.

Terima kasih Daniel Craig kerana menjadi agen 007.

Skala:6/10
Translated Text:
The finale of James Bond may bring you to tears and I won't tell you why.

Thank you Daniel Craig for being the agent of 007.

Scale: 6/10

Text:
Selain itu, cip pemprosesan ini juga bakal hadir dengan dua kategori iaitu berprestasi tinggi dan rendah.

Sesuatu agak mengejutkan apabila cip berprestasi tinggi mempunyai prestasi sama seperti Apple M1 pada MacBook dan Mac Mini.
Translated Text:
In addition, this processing chip will also come with two categories, namely high and low performance.

Something is quite surprising when a high-performance chip has the same performance as the Apple M1 on the MacBook and Mac Mini.

Text:
Jika benar laporan yang dikeluarkan, maka Apple bakal maju setapak berbanding pesaing lain terutama Meta dan Microsoft dalam penciptaan set kepala AR.

Menurut Ming-Chi Kuo, misi Apple adalah untuk menjadi set kepala AR pengganti kepada iPhone dalam tempoh 10 tahun mendatang.
Translated Text:
If the released report is true, then Apple will be one step ahead of other competitors, especially Meta and Microsoft in the creation of AR headsets.

According to Ming-Chi Kuo, Apple's mission is to become an AR headset that replaces the iPhone within the next 10 years.

Text:
Selain cip pemprosesan, set kepala AR bakal menggunakan paparan skrin mikro OLED 4K daripada Sony.

Set kepala AR ini dijangka diperkenalkan pada suku keempat tahun hadapan.
Translated Text:
In addition to the processing chip, the AR headset will use a 4K OLED micro screen display from Sony.

This AR headset is expected to be introduced in the fourth quarter of next year.

Text:
Sejujurnya saya menaruh harapan tinggi pada inovasi baharu daripada Apple.

Sebelum ini saya telah menceritakan tentang perkembangan realiti terimbuh yang bermula daripada perisian dan perkakasan.
Translated Text:
I honestly have high hopes for new innovations from Apple.

Previously I have told about the development of augmented reality that starts from software and hardware.

Text:
Pada awal pengenalan, Apple lebih memfokuskan kepada perisian pada iPhone 8 dan iPhone X.

Kemudian inovasi tersebut dikembangkan dengan penciptaan LiDAR pada iPad Pro (2020) dan ke atas serta iPhone 12 dan iPhone 13 segmen andalan.
Translated Text:
At the beginning of the introduction, Apple focused more on the software on the iPhone 8 and iPhone X.

Then the innovation was expanded with the creation of LiDAR on the iPad Pro (2020) and above as well as the flagship iPhone 12 and iPhone 13 segments.

Text:
Walaupun penggunaan teknologi AR dan LiDAR kurang mendapat sambutan dalam kalangan pengguna.

Apple berani untuk membuat perubahan kepada penciptaan sebuah set kepala AR.
Translated Text:
Although the use of AR and LiDAR technology is less popular among users.

Apple dared to make changes to the creation of an AR headset.

Text:
Saya percaya set kepala AR akan bergantung kepada sumber kuasa daripada palam elektrik.

Agak mustahil set kepala AR bergantung kepada bateri disebabkan cip pemprosesan yang memerlukan tenaga yang tinggi.
Translated Text:
I believe the AR headset will rely on the power source from the electrical plug.

It is quite impossible for the AR headset to depend on the battery due to the processing chip that requires a lot of energy.

Text:
Konklusinya, kita sekarang bakal memasuki era baharu dalam penciptaan realiti terimbuh dan maya.

Tidak dipastikan sama ada kita boleh menerima perkembangan ini atau skeptikal pada revolusi baharu yang bakal bermula tidak lama lagi.
Translated Text:
In conclusion, we are now about to enter a new era in the creation of augmented and virtual reality.

It is uncertain whether we can accept this development or be skeptical of the new revolution that will soon begin.

Text:
Saya tidak pertikai berhubung isu tiruan. Cuma terdapat segelintir Penjual cuba menipu Pembeli dengan menganggap AirPods Pro tersebut asli sedangkan ia dusta belaka.

Penipuan ini dikaburkan dengan kualiti AirPods Pro yang seakan asli.
Translated Text:
I am not arguing about the fake issue. It's just that there are a few Sellers trying to deceive Buyers by thinking that the AirPods Pro are genuine when they are just lies.

This deception is obscured by the seemingly genuine quality of the AirPods Pro.

Fitur pembatalan hingar aktif, Spatial serta paparan pada Widget juga turut tersedia sekali gus membuatkan Pembeli percaya bahawa AirPods Pro tersebut asli.

Text:
AirPods Pro tersebut boleh dibeli serendah RM70 secara dalam talian serta kedai aksesori. 

Tidak mustahil Penjual tersebut boleh menaikkan harga AirPods Pro sehingga RM700 memandangkan harga rasmi AirPods Pro RM1,099.
