It is not impossible that the Seller can raise the price of AirPods Pro up to RM700 considering the official price of AirPods Pro is RM1,099.

Text:
Lambakan AirPods Pro terpakai di pasaran turut membawa kepada penipuan yang lebih meluas. 

Secara dasarnya agak sukar untuk dibezakan AirPods Pro tiruan dan asli jika dilihat melalui ciri fizikal.
Translated Text:
Dumping used AirPods Pro on the market also leads to more widespread fraud.

In principle, it is quite difficult to distinguish fake and original AirPods Pro if you look at the physical characteristics.

Text:
Gambar kiri menunjukkan AirPods Pro asli, manakala kanan tiruan. AirPods Pro asli menunjukkan sedikit perbezaan dari segi perkataan. 

AirPods Pro tiruan menggunakan perkataan "with Wireless" dan "Paired AirPods" manakala AirPods Pro asli disebaliknya. https://t.co/du4LhRiV1O
Translated Text:
The left picture shows the original AirPods Pro, while the right is a fake. The original AirPods Pro show little difference in terms of wording.

The fake AirPods Pro use the words "with Wireless" and "Paired AirPods" while the original AirPods Pro are on the back. https://t.co/du4LhRiV1O

Text: Pada bahagian kenyataan model juga terdapat perbezaan. Gambar sebelah kiri adalah AirPods Pro asli, manakala kanan AirPods Pro tiruan. https://t.co/UeNFJmnX54
Translated Text: There is also a difference in the statement part of the model. The picture on the left is the original AirPods Pro, while the right is a fake AirPods Pro. https://t.co/UeNFJmnX54

Text:
Satu perkara yang membuatkan saya kagum dengan AirPods Pro tiruan adalah semakan warranti. 

Jika disemak di laman rasmi Apple, jelas menunjukkan nombor siri sepadan dengan AirPods Pro tiruan https://t.co/O9ZLBtjS95
Translated Text:
One thing that impressed me about the fake AirPods Pro was the warranty check.

If checked on Apple's official site, it clearly shows the serial number matches the fake AirPods Pro https://t.co/O9ZLBtjS95

Text:
Terdapat beberapa kemungkinan mengapa AirPods Pro tiruan dapat disahkan nombor siri tersebut asli. 

Salah satunya berkemungkinan kilang yang menghasilkan AirPods Pro tiruan telah menggunakan nombor siri AirPods Pro yang asli untuk mengaburi  mata pembeli.
Translated Text:
There are several possibilities why a counterfeit AirPods Pro can be verified as having a genuine serial number.

One of them is the possibility that factories producing fake AirPods Pro have used the serial number of the original AirPods Pro to deceive buyers.

Text:
Berdasarkan pascanilai yang telah saya buat. Sejujurnya terlalu sukar untuk dibezakan antara AirPods Pro asli dan tiruan. 

Kita memerlukan sedikit ilmu dan kepakaran dalam membuat penilaian tersebut.
Translated Text:
Based on the post-evaluation I have made. It's honestly too hard to tell the difference between genuine and fake AirPods Pro.

We need a little knowledge and expertise in making the assessment.

Text:
Tiada masalah untuk sesiapa membeli AirPods Pro tiruan.

Cuma saya kuatir terdapat segelintir pengguna tertipu dengan Penjual yang menjual AirPods Pro yang kononnya asli.
Translated Text:
No problem for anyone to buy fake AirPods Pro.

I'm just worried that there are a few users who are being deceived by Sellers who are selling AirPods Pro that are supposedly genuine.

Text:
Isu ciplak ini sudah lama. Sebelum ini  kabel lightning juga telah menjadi sasaran. 

Mereka berjaya klon cip yang terkandung dalam kabel lightning. Ini bermakna iPhone tidak dapat mengesan bahawa kabel tersebut tiruan.
Translated Text:
This plagiarism issue has been around for a long time. Previously, lightning cables had also been targeted.

They managed to clone the chip contained in the lightning cable. This means that the iPhone cannot detect that the cable is fake.

Text:
Maka peluang ini digunakan oleh segelintir Penjual untuk menipu Pembeli. 

Antara modus operandi mereka termasuklah menggunakan nama "Foxconn".
Translated Text:
So this opportunity is used by a few Sellers to cheat the Buyers.

Among their modus operandi include using the name "Foxconn".

Text:
Namun penipuan ini tidak berpanjangan memandangkan ramai pengguna menghadapi masalah pada kabel lightning setelah kemas kini iOS baharu. 

Seperti biasa, Penjual akan menyalahkan kemas kini iOS, sedangkan kemas kini tersebut telah perangkap kabel lightning tiruan.
Translated Text:
But this scam didn't last long as many users faced problems with the lightning cable after the new iOS update.

As always, the Seller will blame the iOS update, when the update has been a fake lightning cable trap.

Text:
Perisian tegar (firmware) pada AirPods Pro juga saya lihat sukar untuk diciplak. 

Jika AirPods Pro tiruan mampu mengemaskini perisian tegar, bermakna mereka berjaya mencipta produk hampir sempurna asli.
Translated Text:
The firmware on AirPods Pro is also difficult to plagiarize.

If the fake AirPods Pro are able to update the firmware, it means they succeeded in creating an almost perfect original product.

Text:
Penyelesaian tuntas bagi isu ini adalah dengan membeli di AAR yang sah seperti @SwitchTM, @MachinesAPR dan lain-lain. 

Jika mahu beli secara dalam talian. Sila beli di LazMall atau Shopee Mall.
Translated Text:
A complete solution to this issue is to buy at a legitimate AAR like @SwitchTM, @MachinesAPR and others.

If you want to buy online. Please buy at LazMall or Shopee Mall.

Text:
Jangan mudah terpedaya dengan mulut manis Penjual yang tidak disahkan oleh Apple Malaysia. 

Tiada salahnya untuk anda beli AirPods Pro tiruan, asalkan anda tahu bahawa ia tiruan.
Translated Text:
Do not be easily fooled by the sweet mouth of Sellers who are not verified by Apple Malaysia.

There is nothing wrong with buying fake AirPods Pro, as long as you know that they are fake.

Text:
Jika mahu beli yang asli, maka ikut saranan saya seperti di atas. 

Tidak perlu jadi detektif Conan untuk siasat yang mana asli atau tiruan, kecuali anda memang seorang yang mahir tentang selok belok AirPods Pro tiruan.
Translated Text:
If you want to buy the original, then follow my advice as above.

No need to be detective Conan to investigate which is genuine or fake, unless you're an expert on the ins and outs of fake AirPods Pro.

Text:
AirPods Pro tiruan akan mengalami fasa evolusi sepanjang masa. 

Mungkin apa yang saya nyatakan ini telah dibaiki oleh mereka untuk mengaburi mata kasar kita. Berhati-hati bila membeli produk dan aksesori Apple.
Translated Text:
The fake AirPods Pro will undergo an evolution phase all the time.

Maybe what I mentioned has been corrected by them to obscure our eyes. Be careful when buying Apple products and accessories.

Text:
Jangan kerana harga yang dijual oleh mereka murah, terus anda buta mata dan hati. 

Bila jadi mangsa penipuan, mula marah dan salahkan pihak lain. Sedangkan ia berpunca daripada sikap kita sendiri. 

SEKADAR PANDANGAN
Translated Text:
Don't just because the price they sell is cheap, keep blinding your eyes and heart.

When you become a victim of fraud, start to get angry and blame the other party. Whereas it stems from our own attitude.

JUST A VIEW
